<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='865000' id='t-865000'>The uncle went back to his family,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='867000' id='t-867000'>and Natasha and Tim and Gene and I went out to dinner.</span>
