<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='883000' id='t-883000'>This is the third night we were in Korea.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885000' id='t-885000'>The first night we'd gotten a room for the kids right next to us.</span>
