<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='975000' id='t-975000'>and the hotel's on fire.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='977000' id='t-977000'>So, I run over to Gene, and I wake him up,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='979000' id='t-979000'>and I say, &quot;Gene, don't freak out, I think the hotel's on fire.&quot;</span>
