<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='988000' id='t-988000'>So, we're trying to get Natasha up, and we can't talk to her.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='992000' id='t-992000'>And you know what kids are like when they've been asleep for like an hour,</span>
