19:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1139000' id='t-1139000'>And then 12 hours later, we rented a car, as we had planned to,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1142000' id='t-1142000'>and drove back to Natasha's village.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1144000' id='t-1144000'>And we kept saying, &quot;Do you realize we were dying in a hotel fire,</span>
