<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1175000' id='t-1175000'>This is the last picture before Gene and Tim headed back.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1179000' id='t-1179000'>The adoption people told us it was going to take a year for the adoption to go through.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1184000' id='t-1184000'>Like, what could you do for a year?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1186000' id='t-1186000'>So I found out the name of every official on both the Korean and American side,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1189000' id='t-1189000'>and I photographed them, and told them</span>
