<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1194000' id='t-1194000'>And four months later, the adoption papers came through.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1198000' id='t-1198000'>This is saying goodbye to everybody at the orphanage.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1201000' id='t-1201000'>This is Father Keene with Natasha at the bus stop.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1204000' id='t-1204000'>Her great aunt at the airport.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1206000' id='t-1206000'>I had a wonderful deal with Cathay Pacific airlines for many years,</span>
