<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1214000' id='t-1214000'>It was like the ultimate perk.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1216000' id='t-1216000'>And the pilot, I actually knew -- because they used to let me sit</span>
