<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1232000' id='t-1232000'>This is 28 hours later in Atlanta. It's a very long flight.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1235000' id='t-1235000'>Just to make things even crazier,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1237000' id='t-1237000'>Gail, Natasha's new mom, was three days away</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1239000' id='t-1239000'>from giving birth to her own daughter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1242000' id='t-1242000'>So you know, if you were writing this, you'd say,</span>
