<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1247000' id='t-1247000'>This is the first night showing Natasha her new cousins and uncles and aunts.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1251000' id='t-1251000'>Gene and Gail know everyone in Atlanta --</span>
